title: (Fri Early Bird) Luke Combs on his New Album and Baby + We Start A New Season of Easy Trivia + Fun Fact Friday: The Hit TV Show HBO Passed On
itunes:title: (Fri Early Bird) Luke Combs on his New Album and Baby + We Start A New Season of Easy Trivia + Fun Fact Friday: The Hit TV Show HBO Passed On
description:
Luke Combs is in studio to talk about his new album, who he trusts in his life to tell him if something he writes is good or not and talks about his new baby! After last week winner was crowed, we start a new season of Easy Trivia! Amy shares her 5 fun facts!
